<br>
To create a table in ezboard, you need to do 2 things.  First, you need to make sure all your html is on ONE line (no line breaks).  Otherwise you'll get about a million blank lines before your table.<br>
<br>
Second, you need to put your table between<br>
<!--EZCODE HTML START--> <!--EZCODE HTML END--> tags and make sure your EzCodes checkbox is checked.<br>
