<br>
For the static (non-wandering) named mobs that drop quest pieces, will they always spawn in the same, *unique* spot?<br>
<br>
For example, in the hopper cave in Dawnshroud I have seen almost all of the named rockhoppers and some more than once.  I have always seen the same name in the same spot and never any other named in that spot, which leads me to believe that above statement is true.<br>
<br>
However, someone mentioned in this thread that three different named thought horrors could spawn in the same spot, which obviously rejects the above statement.<br>
<br>
I'm seeking the Dusty Spire Spirit spiecifically, and so far I have found a named for every spot on the ground floor minus one (that spot being the one directly under the staircase).  Should I keep clearing out the floor or camp that one spot to continue my search?<br>
